369
00:30:58,980 --> 00:31:02,000
It's not that he really doesn't have the seven emotions and six desires.

370
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:05,210
It's just that his name is not in the Three Lives Stone.

371
00:31:05,210 --> 00:31:09,220
No matter what happens,

372
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:12,390
