373
00:31:12,390 --> 00:31:16,650
Young Highness, do you know what an ill-fated relationship is?

374
00:31:17,850 --> 00:31:21,590
It's just like what the both of you went through in the Mortal Realm.

375
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:26,640
The love between you and the emperor will never have a good ending.

