00:31:57,120 --> 00:32:02,110
Emperor Dong Hua, where is your name?

380
00:32:02,110 --> 00:32:04,160
Where?

381
00:32:07,950 --> 00:32:10,350
Bai Fengjiu.

382
00:32:16,570 --> 00:32:19,720
It can't be.

383
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:22,320
It can't be.

384
00:32:24,250 --> 00:32:27,330
How can this be?

385
00:32:27,330 --> 00:32:29,840
It can't be.

386
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:32,840
How can this be?

387
00:32:39,780 --> 00:32:43,230
I love Emperor Dong Hua.

388
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:50,190
Young Highness, listen to my advice.

389
00:32:50,190 --> 00:32:54,570
If you are still obsessed with this and going against Heaven's will,

390
00:32:54,570 --> 00:33:00,310
