391
00:33:00,310 --> 00:33:05,750
Your number of years of being together in the Mortal Realm is only just a few days of fate in Heaven.

392
00:33:05,750 --> 00:33:09,880
This has caused him to lose his divine power.

393
00:33:13,170 --> 00:33:15,520
Since it's only temporary,

394
00:33:15,520 --> 00:33:20,000
in two years or so, he will recover his divine power.

395
00:33:20,940 --> 00:33:23,520
But this is a warning.

396
00:33:23,520 --> 00:33:30,920
If you are bent on being by his side, I wonder what kind of bad karma you and the emperor will have.

397
00:33:33,290 --> 00:33:36,670
Young Highness, repent and be saved.

