Don't follow me.

438
00:37:14,250 --> 00:37:15,940
High God!

439
00:37:15,940 --> 00:37:18,450
High God Zhe Yan!

440
00:37:18,450 --> 00:37:22,490
Fourth Uncle! Fourth Uncle!

441
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:26,990
I forgot they all went to Kunlun Void.

442
00:37:29,470 --> 00:37:31,200
Great Lady!

443
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:33,080
Great Lady!

444
00:37:33,080 --> 00:37:36,720
Great Lady! Great Lady!

445
00:37:37,410 --> 00:37:40,340
You two are... Isn't this Seventeenth's niece?

446
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:42,130
Yes. She's our Young Highness.

447
00:37:42,130 --> 00:37:44,870
I'm Mi Gu, the Junior Immortal who serves her in fox den.

448
00:37:44,870 --> 00:37:47,270
She cut off her tail.

449
00:37:47,270 --> 00:37:49,210
She's having a high fever and is unconscious.

450
00:37:49,210 --> 00:37:54,310
I can't find High God Zhe Yan so I can only come here to find Great Lady.

451
00:37:54,310 --> 00:37:56,730
Come.

452
00:37:56,730 --> 00:37:58,750
Come with me.

453
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:12,610
Why aren't they here? Why aren't they here yet?

454
00:38:12,610 --> 00:38:15,870
Don't worry. I already instructed someone to find them.

455
00:38:16,550 --> 00:38:17,880
Is she awake?

456
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:21,350
