460
00:38:28,140 --> 00:38:29,800
It's all because of Emperor Dong Hua.

461
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:32,600
Every time she's hurt, it's because of that emperor.

462
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:34,180
What do you mean?

463
00:38:34,180 --> 00:38:41,760
When Si Ming brought her back, he said she cut off her tail.

464
00:38:41,760 --> 00:38:44,160
Fourth Older Brother, look at this child.

465
00:38:44,160 --> 00:38:47,330
She seriously doesn't care if she throws away her life.

466
00:38:47,330 --> 00:38:49,820
Hurry and stop the pain!

467
00:38:49,820 --> 00:38:54,380
The pain from cutting off the tail is extremely painful till the point of death.

468
00:38:59,780 --> 00:39:01,380
I have already stopped the pain.

469
00:39:01,380 --> 00:39:02,800
Don't say anything.

470
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:05,050
You should leave.

471
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:28,190
Why are you here?

472
00:39:28,190 --> 00:39:32,440
Young Fifth, be polite when you talk to the emperor.

473
00:39:33,290 --> 00:39:37,080
Even more so, when it's not his fault.

474
00:39:37,080 --> 00:39:39,520
You are not aware, too. The Three Lives Stone...

475
00:39:39,520 --> 00:39:42,100
So what about the Three Lives Stone?

476
00:39:44,240 --> 00:39:48,920
Emperor, you distinctly knew that you couldn't incur any love debt,

477
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:52,170
