478
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:58,240
Our tribe is the type to never give up.

479
00:39:58,240 --> 00:40:01,240
Whoever we identify with, we will never change our minds.

480
00:40:01,240 --> 00:40:04,540
You made her fall for you,

